        "body_content": "Home\nVehicles\nSoftware\nCharging\nService\nFinancing\nGet Updates\n\nFord Pro™ Telematics1\n\nIt Works for Business\n\nFrom oil life status and tire pressure to driver performance and vehicle location, it’s amazing how connected you can be to your modern fleet. The no-charge Ford Pro™ Telematics Essentials2 and subscription-based Ford Pro™ Telematics are easy-to-use web applications that collect and interpret key data from your fleet vehicles, then provide insights that will help you get the most from your vehicles and from the people who drive them.\n\nActivate Essentials Now\nContact Us\nDisclosure(s)\nWhat does Ford Pro Telematics Do?\n\nGPS FLEET TRACKING\n\nYour Ford Pro™ Telematics software includes GPS-driven fleet tracking so you can find out where your drivers are on a route through geofencing and live maps, so you can deliver real-time updates to customers awaiting the arrival of your goods or services.\n\nVEHICLE HEALTH ALERTS\n\nA healthy fleet is a productive fleet. With Ford Pro™ Telematics, you’ll have a clear outlook on the status of your fleet from the convenience of your office seat. Know, almost instantly, if a vehicle needs an oil change, if there’s a recall, when a warning light comes on and more.\n\nDRIVER BEHAVIOR INSIGHTS\n\nAt the wheel of every vehicle in your fleet is a driver. Driver behavior insights put you in the passenger seat, delivering the kinds of observations — like harsh braking or acceleration — that can help improve driver performance and safety on the road.\n\nFUEL EFFICIENCY ANALYSIS\n\nFuel is one of your largest expenses. With Ford Pro™ Telematics, you can monitor fuel consumption and idling time, then identify ways to improve efficiency. What’s more, it will even deliver data about how adding hybrid or all-electric vehicles to your fleet can bolster your bottom line.\n\nFORD PRO™ TELEMATICS DRIVE APP\n\nThe Ford Pro™ Telematics Drive app provides your drivers with a fast and easy way to let you know if there are any issues with a fleet. Just as importantly, the app provides a consistent pre-trip checklist, making it possible to identify any issues before the vehicle is even on the road.\n\n1 - 3 of 5\nTelematics Essentials\nTelematics\nTelematics Essentials\n\nStart With Essentials at No Cost\n\nActivate the indispensable features from Ford Pro™ Telematics Essentials.3 Know the health and status of every vehicle in your fleet to stay ahead of unexpected repair costs and unwanted downtime. Enrollment with Ford Pro™ Telematics Essentials is simple and comes at no additional charge with every Ford fleet vehicle. So, what are you waiting for?\n\nDisclosure(s)\nActivate Essentials Now\n\nFord Pro™ Telematics Essentials5\n\nAvailable now, at absolutely no cost to you:\n\n\n\t100% Complimentary: For the life of your Ford fleet vehicle.\n\tEasy-to-Read Ford Pro™ Telematics Dashboard Interface\n\tVehicle Health Alerts\n\tPlanned Maintenance Tracking\n\tDealer Scheduling Capability\n\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\n\nActivate Essentials Now\n\nFord Pro™ Telematics6\n\nUpgrade now for only $20.00/month/vehicle. You’ll get all the benefits of Ford Pro Telematics Essentials, plus:\n\n\n\tDriver Behavior Insights\n\tEasy-to-Read Ford Pro™ Telematics Dashboard Interface\n\tVehicle Alerts\n\tPlanned Maintenance Tracking\n\tService History\n\tReal-Time Location Tracking & Event Tracking\n\tGPS Fleet Tracking & Location History\n\tFuel Efficiency, Idling & Waste\n\tFord Pro™ Telematics Drive App\n\tNon-Ford Vehicle Support\n\nSchedule A Demo\n\nStay in the Know About All Things Ford Pro™\n\nGet Updates\nCalifornia Residents\n\nExercise your rights under the California Consumer Privacy Act here.\n\nDo Not Sell My Personal Information\nSite MapGlossarySite FeedbackContact UsAccessibilityTerms & ConditionsPrivacyCookie SettingsYour CA Privacy RightsAdChoicesThird-Party Trademarks\n\n\n© 2022 Ford Motor Company\n\nThis website uses cookies to enhance user experience and to analyze performance and traffic on our website. We also share information about your use of our site with our social media, advertising, and analytics partners. Privacy Policy\n\nCookie Settings",
